# ── MAII frontend — build-time configuration (Vite) ─────────────────────────────
# Public base URL of the deployed maha-copilot backend (the maha-copilot/ FastAPI app).
#
# Vite INLINES this at build time, so it must be set BEFORE `npm run build`:
#     VITE_MAHA_COPILOT_URL=https://copilot.yourdomain.gov.in npm run build
# or copy this file to `.env.production` and uncomment the line below.
#
# To change the URL WITHOUT rebuilding, edit public/maha-config.js on the server instead
# (that value takes priority). Leave unset for local dev (defaults to http://127.0.0.1:8000).
#
# VITE_MAHA_COPILOT_URL=https://copilot.yourdomain.gov.in
